                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                                        <date>Oct 29/5609</date>-</p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>-</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">My dear sir-</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">At the request of the Montreal Committee for<lb/>\n                                        the relief of the Persecuted Persian Jews I beg to\n                                        request<lb/> you to take <add>?</add> for the <add>?</add>\n                                        of the republication<lb/> in any of the\n                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> papers of the\n                                        name of <persName>R Nissim ben<add>?</add><lb/>\n                                                  Solomon</persName> an accredited messenger from\n                                        our oppressed Persian brethren<lb/> in connection with a\n                                        lecture delivered here by myself in their behalf.<lb/> The\n                                        publication of his name he subsequently considers may\n                                        prove<lb/> injurious to him, and altho the committee\n                                                  (<add>?</add> enter into<lb/> his fears yet they\n                                        bow in deference to them.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Again requesting you to give the above your<lb/>\n                                        immediate and best attention I am dear sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">Truly yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The above, dear Friend, bears an official aspect.\n                                                  <persName>R Nissim</persName><lb/> in whom I take\n                                        a great interest, fears that the news may go back<lb/> to\n                                                  <placeName>Russia</placeName> that he has been\n                                        telling naughty things of them, I<lb/>\n                                        <sic>dont</sic> fear any thing of the sort. Let me hear your\n                                        opinion—<lb/> would you like a notice or <add>?</add> of the\n                                        article—I shall<lb/> answer your last as soon as I possibly\n                                        can. I have been and<lb/> am yet too busy to do so. Till\n                                        then <add>שלום</add></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><hi rend=\"underline\">Dont give the above publicly\n                                                  till I write you again</hi>. <persName\n                                                  role=\"author\">ADS</persName>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3fx74f2f/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
